data.description: Farm land is getting harder and harder to find, but this listing has it all! The spacious 5,500 sq ft ranch style home with basement has plenty of room and then some. Sitting on 13.39 acres of land, this property has space for plenty of family or friends of both the two and four legged variety! There's even a pond on the property for your cattle to relax in after a hard day grazing in the pre-fenced pastures. The property features many recent updates such as new toilets and vanities in each bathroom; new exterior doors; new floors in the bathrooms, laundry rooms, and kitchen; new attic insulation; new countertops; and a new gas range, fridge and microwave. The finished basement currently has a partition to add even more rooms, but the sellers are happy to take that down if you're more into an open concept sort of space. Part of the basement is currently decorated with paintings of some very famous toys (see photos), but the sellers are willing to paint over that if needed. If there's anything that can rival the size of this home's living space, it is the property's incredible amount of storage space. Whether you have a lot of family, a lot of friends, or some cattle to tend, this property is perfect for you. From a gas stove to a backup spring for water, this farm just has too many features to list at once. Come take a look today; the view of the mountains is sure to impress! Buyer and buyer agents to validate all details. Call today!
